{
  "id": "RAW_77ae72ba",
  "title": "Dify × 阿里云计算巢：实现分钟级部署，企业级高可用更省心",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5MDkyOTY3NA==&mid=2247487738&idx=2&sn=ff979b08bf54eb47e47e6233679206fc",
  "date": "2026-01-09 03:04:00",
  "author": "Dify",
  "siteName": "Dify",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f83fef4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fmmecoa_jpg%2FftnoqhiaHUyibNtSzzHezP1NZULq7ibtQl1cRrIJPFsrpARgiaa4hUPlZVVPYcP8OapUOkyibUKFdtDO46Gmz8OgbJA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>解锁高可用、零运维的企业级 AI 应用部署新体验。</p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">Dify 使得 AI 应用开发变得前所未有地简单：拖拽式编排 Agent、一键接入知识库、快速发布 API，即使非技术人员，也能参与智能应用创新。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">但当企业真正要落地时，挑战才刚刚开始。</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: flex-end;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:38px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">01</span></span></em></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;align-self: flex-end;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 0px 0px 9px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:20px;\">传统私有化交付的四大典型痛点</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">1）资源分散，手动开通耗时长</span></span></strong></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">需要分别创建并准备 ACK 集群、OSS 存储、RDS 数据库、Redis 缓存、AnalyticDB 向量库等至少 5 类云资源，流程繁琐且容易遗漏。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">2）配置复杂，依赖人工调通</span></span></strong></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">组件之间需要手动配置 VPC、安全组、网络策略、IP 白名单、服务账号权限等，一处细节出错，就可能导致服务无法互通，排查成本高。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">3）环境不一致，部署成功率不稳定</span></span></strong></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">Python 依赖冲突、镜像版本不匹配、环境变量遗漏等问题频发。同一套脚本在不同客户环境中可能出现截然不同的结果，交付稳定性难以保障。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">4）运维割裂，管理成本持续攀升</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">资源分散在多个控制台：升级、扩缩容、监控、备份需要跨系统操作，故障定位难、协作成本高，长期运维负担显著。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">这些“看不见的工程成本”，常常让一个本应快速上线的 AI 项目，陷入数天甚至数周的部署与联调周期。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">现在，这些问题可以被系统性解决。</span></span></strong></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: flex-end;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:38px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">02</span></span></em></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;align-self: flex-end;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 0px 0px 9px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:20px;\">计算巢下的 Dify 的方案有何不同</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">依托阿里云计算巢，Dify 企业版与云资源实现深度融合，将复杂的资源准备与联通配置封装为标准化、自动化、可审计的一键交付流程，实现更接近“开箱即用”的部署体验。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">对比传统方式，你不再需要逐项完成以下工作：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">手动开通 ACK、OSS、RDS PostgreSQL、Redis、AnalyticDB 等资源。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">逐项配置安全组、VPC、IP 白名单，确保服务互通。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">下载镜像、处理依赖冲突、调试环境变量。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">部署后再分别搭建监控、备份、扩容、升级流程。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">通过计算巢，上述步骤被统一编排为一套交付能力，核心流程体现在四个方面：</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">一键拉起完整 Dify 环境</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">计算巢自动创建并配置所需资源：ACK 容器服务、OSS 存储、RDS 数据库、Redis 缓存、向量引擎（Tablestore 或 AnalyticDB 等）自动部署 Dify 服务，大幅减少人工介入与交付不确定性。</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">统一视角，集中运维</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">所有 Dify 相关资源归属同一资源栈，可在计算巢控制台实现一屏管理，避免在多个控制台之间频繁切换，显著提升运维效率。</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">极速部署，按需弹性扩展</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">ECS 部署模式：最快 5 分钟完成上线，适用于测试验证或轻量生产场景。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">ACS 弹性集群模式：支持自动扩缩容，从容应对业务峰值与资源波动。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">持续演进，升级更省心</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">计算巢会持续同步 Dify 企业版能力与内置模型版本，用户可在控制台自助完成版本升级，减少重复部署与迁移成本。</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: flex-end;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:38px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">03</span></span></em></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;align-self: flex-end;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 0px 0px 9px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:20px;\">向量数据库选型的隐性成本</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">企业在部署 Dify Agent 应用时，向量数据库往往是“卡点”之一：</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">是自建 Milvus、Weaviate，还是选择商业向量服务？</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">自建意味着运维复杂、扩缩容困难；第三方服务又可能带来兼容性、成本结构或数据主权方面的考量。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">阿里云表格存储（Tablestore）提供了一种更轻量、更集成的选择：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">原生支持向量字段，并支持图索引能力</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">免运维、自动扩缩容，按量付费</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">深度集成阿里云生态，可与 Dify 通过计算巢一键打通</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">支持混合检索（向量 + 标量 + 全文），满足复杂 Agent 场景</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">在计算巢交付的 Dify 企业版中，用户可按业务规模灵活选择向量引擎，无论是Tablestore 还是 AnalyticDB，均已完成预集成与预配置，避免在选型、对接与联调上耗费额外精力。</span></span></p>\n   <blockquote class=\"js_blockquote_wrap\">\n    <div class=\"js_blockquote_digest\">\n     <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">如果想了解 Tablestore，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">点击查看更多：</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"blockquote_info js_blockquote_source\" data-json=\"%7B%22type%22%3A%22out%22%2C%22article%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22from%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aliyun.com%2Fproduct%2Fots%22%7D\"><span class=\"blockquote_other\"><a href=\"https://www.aliyun.com/product/ots\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.aliyun.com/product/ots</a></span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"8 9 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: flex-end;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size:38px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">04</span></em></strong></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;align-self: flex-end;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 0px 0px 9px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-style: normal;\">三步开启企业级 Dify 体验</span></span></em></strong></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">在阿里云计算巢上部署 Dify 企业版，全程可视化、零代码，普通用户也能轻松完成：</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">第